precis:
Amendments to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS which permit The Mortgage
Insurance Corporation of Canada, or any other mortgage insurer who enters
into a similar Agreement with the Crown, to deduct both the amounts paid
into a mortgage guarantee fund and the earnings of that fund from their
taxable earnings.
